		       <SETG LIT T>
		       <FSET ,HERE ,ONBIT>
		       <FSET ,DARK-OBJECT ,DARKBIT>
		       <MOVE ,DARK-OBJECT ,DARK>
		       <TELL
"Good start to the day. Pity it's going to be the worst one of your
life. The light is now on." CR CR>
