"You have failed to issue one of the small set of commands that the
guards' military intelligences are trained to understand." CR>
			      <FUCKING-CLEAR>)>)
		      (T
		       <COND (<HELD? ,BABEL-FISH ,PROTAGONIST>
			      <TELL "\"Resistance is useless!\"" CR>)
			     (T
			      <TELL "\"I">
			      <PRODUCE-GIBBERISH 1>
