		       <FUCKING-CLEAR>)>)
	       (<AND <EQUAL? ,HERE ,CAPTAINS-QUARTERS>
		     <VERB? TELL HELLO THANK>>
		<PERFORM ,V?TELL ,VOGON-CAPTAIN>
		<RTRUE>)
